Package: bounceR
Title: A Cricket package to make Hawkeye data accessible
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Richard",
           family = "Little",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "alittlefitness@gmail.com")
Description: bounceR provides a set of functions to extract Hawkeye data for Cricket from json files on the ICC and BCCI webpages, 
    turning them into tidy data for analysis. Current data extracted includes Test matches, ODI and IPL T20 competitions.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.1.1
Imports: 
    curl,
    dplyr,
    stringr,
    tidyr,
    jsonlite
